1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:57,470
Oden Was Meant to Boil

3
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:18,530
I wasn't expecting a war.

4
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:21,540
You seem a bit too prepared!

5
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:23,660
How did you know we were coming?!

6
00:02:26,830 --> 00:02:30,710
Perhaps there is a spy in your castle.

7
00:02:34,180 --> 00:02:39,930
I'd hate to see my newly built
stronghold become a battlefield,

8
00:02:39,930 --> 00:02:42,350
so I came to you instead!

9
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:48,860
It was all a lie, right, Kaido?!

10
00:02:48,860 --> 00:02:50,900
That's right.

11
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:53,900
It was all a lie.

12
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:58,240
We felt we were at a disadvantage back then.

13
00:02:58,450 --> 00:03:01,870
If you had joined forces
with Hyogoro after your homecoming,

14
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:07,330
the samurai and yakuza of Wano
would've all risen against us!

15
00:03:07,330 --> 00:03:11,210
Our manpower was more limited at the time.

16
00:03:11,210 --> 00:03:18,260
And if you were ready to sacrifice anything
like the loose cannon I'd heard about...

17
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:23,520
it would've been a tough battle.

18
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:30,440
But you believed Orochi's words and chose
a path where no one would get hurt.

19
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:35,450
Newgate and Roger were
definitely that kind of pirate...

20
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:40,070
Strong as hell
but suckers in their own right.

21
00:03:40,070 --> 00:03:42,410
You're just like them!

22
00:03:42,410 --> 00:03:44,660
A fool who kept dancing!

23
00:03:44,660 --> 00:03:49,000
Naked, derided, and scorned!

24
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:56,720
You've lost the dignity of the Kozuki Clan!

25
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:07,810
I do not regret my choice that day.

26
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:11,690
It is time we discussed the future.

27
00:04:37,590 --> 00:04:40,130
Wait! I didn't know the samurai
were this strong!

28
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:41,390
Don't wimp out!

29
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,510
We've got them outnumbered!

30
00:04:45,310 --> 00:04:47,140
Advance, advance!

31
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:49,690
Follow Lord Oden's lead!

32
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:04,200
You're dead!

33
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:08,790
What happened?!

34
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,790
Who did that?

35
00:05:12,290 --> 00:05:16,420
I hope helping you is not too
presumptuous, Lord Oden.

36
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:18,130
You may not remember me,

37
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:21,470
but back when Lord Sukiyaki
was still alive, I was...

38
00:05:22,470 --> 00:05:23,970
Shinobu of the ninja corps?!

39
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:27,470
Yes!

40
00:05:27,470 --> 00:05:28,810
It is I!

41
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:30,850
Why are you all by yourself?

42
00:05:30,850 --> 00:05:32,850
What happened to the others?

43
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:36,020
The other Kozuki ninja...

44
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:39,530
Fukurokuju sold out to Orochi.

45
00:05:40,860 --> 00:05:45,280
I cannot blame those who lost faith
in their fool of a lord.

46
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:51,620
I had always dreamed
of serving you, Lord Oden.

47
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:53,870
I am still a loyal Kozuki ninja!

48
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:56,420
The way forward will be treacherous, Shinobu!

49
00:05:56,420 --> 00:05:58,590
I am well aware!

50
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:00,300
I will follow you to the end!

51
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:02,510
Let us go, then!

52
00:06:03,590 --> 00:06:04,840
Take this!

53
00:06:09,970 --> 00:06:13,440
A messenger came with a letter from Oden.

54
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:17,270
It said, "My wife and children
will be targeted. Please protect them."

55
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:19,150
Dropkick!

56
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:25,030
How dare you!

57
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:26,990
Wait!

58
00:06:26,990 --> 00:06:28,410
Momonosuke...

59
00:06:28,410 --> 00:06:31,620
I mean, Lord Momonosuke is already eight.

60
00:06:32,370 --> 00:06:35,210
Otoki, you have to be prepared.

61
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:41,210
If Oden is bested...

62
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:44,550
this country is finished.

63
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:57,690
This is the first unit. They've wiped us out!

64
00:06:59,770 --> 00:07:03,940
Kozuki Oden is far stronger than we imagined!

65
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,280
This is pathetic!

66
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:11,540
How could it take this long
to finish off eleven samurai?!

67
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:13,830
We have a thousand troops.

68
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:15,580
I can't bear to watch.

69
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,710
I will go!

70
00:07:34,850 --> 00:07:37,560
Blast Breath!

71
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,960
Kozuki Oden!

72
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:10,970
I've been waiting for a man like you!

73
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,640
All I want...

74
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:19,560
is your head!

75
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:28,450
Oden Two-Sword Style:

76
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,830
Halcyon Totsuka!

77
00:08:34,410 --> 00:08:34,540
Hal

78
00:08:34,540 --> 00:08:34,660
Halcyon

79
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:34,790
Halcyon
Tot

80
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:34,870
Halcyon
Totsuka

81
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,080
– Yes!
– Yes!

82
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:53,140
He wounded our invincible Viceroy Kaido?!

83
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:06,320
This is it!

84
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:15,700
Never set foot...

85
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:17,700
in Wano again!

86
00:09:21,170 --> 00:09:22,250
Help!

87
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,130
Father!

88
00:09:24,130 --> 00:09:26,920
Father, save me!

89
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:31,050
Momo!

90
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:55,570
Guess who!

91
00:09:58,450 --> 00:10:00,870
– Lord Oden!
– Lord Oden!

92
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,090
Ashura!

93
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:11,630
Lord Oden...

94
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:28,270
And so ended the legendary battle
of Kozuki Oden and the Red Scabbards.

95
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:40,450
The battle between the Beast Pirates
and the Red Scabbards samurai was so intense,

96
00:10:40,450 --> 00:10:47,420
that the lush forests of Udon continued
to burn until it finally rained five days later.

97
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:51,510
– Mother!
– Mother!

98
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:56,090
When will Father come home?!

99
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:58,350
I made a balloon for him!

100
00:10:58,350 --> 00:11:00,350
Oh, how lovely!

101
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:05,230
Looking forward to his return?

102
00:11:05,230 --> 00:11:08,360
Uh-huh! I wanna play with Father!

103
00:11:16,990 --> 00:11:21,450
Kozuki Oden, the daimyo of Kuri,
and his nine accomplices

104
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:28,790
were charged with rebellion against the shogun
and imprisoned in the Flower Capital.

105
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:34,340
The people were ignorant of his plight
and reacted with cold contempt.

106
00:11:34,340 --> 00:11:35,840
He was already a disappointment.

107
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,300
It's too little, too late.

108
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:40,510
So, does this mean no more
weekly naked dances?

109
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:42,770
That's the only downside!

110
00:11:42,770 --> 00:11:44,600
Hey, be serious!

111
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,680
Oops.

112
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:47,270
Sorry, my bad!

113
00:11:52,110 --> 00:11:53,980
Who is that?

114
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:59,490
She is not one of my retainers!

115
00:11:59,490 --> 00:12:02,080
She must be after my life!

116
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:04,950
Lord Oden?

117
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:08,210
Do not call me that, you pretender!

118
00:12:08,210 --> 00:12:10,880
Keep your lying tongue away, kunoichi!

119
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:25,560
The verdict against
the samurai has been decided!

120
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:38,400
The ten vile samurai, who in recent days
rebelled against Shogun Orochi...

121
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:47,080
are sentenced to public execution
by boiling three days from now!

122
00:12:54,590 --> 00:12:56,710
Three days later...

123
00:12:59,430 --> 00:13:01,840
It's not every day you get to see a boiling!

124
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:04,510
Boiled in oil? It'll be over in a flash!

125
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:06,730
Hurry, or we'll miss it!

126
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:09,180
Stop!

127
00:13:09,810 --> 00:13:12,440
Momonosuke, it hasn't been
tested for poison yet.

128
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,190
Allow me.

129
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,150
Mother...

130
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:22,280
Why would anyone be after my life?

131
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,580
Because your father is a great man...

132
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:30,370
and you are the one who will
one day govern this country.

133
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:34,670
Here you go, Lord Momonosuke
and Lady Hiyori.

134
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:36,550
Time to eat!

135
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:39,590
Brother?

136
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:45,720
Mother!

137
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:53,600
Is it true...? Today, Father will...

138
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:09,290
The public execution of Kozuki Oden
and his nine retainers shall now proceed!

139
00:14:13,420 --> 00:14:16,090
He was no match for Kaido in the end.

140
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:20,960
He was a fool of a lord,
but I thought he was strong!

141
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,880
Everything about him was a letdown, huh?

142
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:46,160
Give me a chance.

143
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:49,660
I must live!

144
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:52,540
Don't be ridiculous!

145
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,920
Begging for your life now is laughable!

146
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,590
Just get in!

147
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:07,300
Hel–

148
00:15:07,300 --> 00:15:09,140
S-Stay back!

149
00:15:14,810 --> 00:15:17,560
The ten of us will enter the pot together.

150
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:25,320
We will stay in for however long you wish,
but after that time limit...

151
00:15:26,530 --> 00:15:28,530
let the survivors go free!

152
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:42,000
You imbecile!

153
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,760
It'll kill you instantly!

154
00:15:53,270 --> 00:15:56,190
Have you lost your mind, Oden?!

155
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:02,020
What a sore loser!

156
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:04,230
Even his final moments are pathetic!

157
00:16:04,610 --> 00:16:07,530
Hey, bring us a clock!

158
00:16:07,530 --> 00:16:08,570
Yes, sir!

159
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:09,870
Wh-What?!

160
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:11,530
H-Hey! Kaido!

161
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:17,500
It sounds fun!

162
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:23,550
This is your defining performance!

163
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:25,760
I won't avert my eyes.

164
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:32,470
You have one hour!

165
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:34,140
We'll see if you last.

166
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:37,350
It'd be risky to stay that long
even in a normal bath!

167
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:43,270
He really is a clown!

168
00:16:44,110 --> 00:16:46,030
Do you give you word?

169
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:47,900
You have it.

170
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:53,410
Wait a minute, Lord Oden!

171
00:16:53,410 --> 00:16:54,790
Lord Oden!

172
00:17:12,010 --> 00:17:13,050
Lord Oden!

173
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:18,100
We must follow our lord!

174
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:22,520
All at once!

175
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:26,020
I will see you all in the next world!

176
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:27,860
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

177
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:39,910
Stay on the board, you guys!

178
00:17:51,170 --> 00:17:53,260
What are you trying to do, Lord Oden?!

179
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:05,610
You must stop this, Lord Oden!

180
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:14,490
Surviving like this would be a disgrace!

181
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:18,740
We should be in your place, Lord Oden!

182
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:20,700
Let us hold you up instead!

183
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:22,290
Lord Oden!

184
00:18:24,210 --> 00:18:27,710
Shut up and stay put!

185
00:18:28,630 --> 00:18:32,050
It is our duty to protect you!

186
00:18:32,050 --> 00:18:34,680
This is an order!

187
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,260
What the hell?!

188
00:18:39,850 --> 00:18:44,100
His retainers aren't even in the oil!

189
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:50,820
But the ten of them are within the pot.

190
00:18:53,450 --> 00:18:56,700
Well played, Oden!

191
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:04,250
Now, let's begin!

192
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,460
Lord Oden...

193
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:15,380
Put us down!

194
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:23,890
What's the matter?

195
00:19:23,890 --> 00:19:26,650
It hasn't been even a minute yet.

196
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:37,030
How can his skin endure it?!

197
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:46,290
It feels like the heat alone will kill me...

198
00:19:46,290 --> 00:19:50,670
If you keep whining,
I'll show you real pain, Raizo!

199
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:53,170
Our only job is to sit up here!

200
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:56,590
Don't move, Cat!

201
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:58,300
It makes it harder to hold!

202
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:06,940
Lord Oden...

203
00:20:10,810 --> 00:20:13,440
I heard this wouldn't take long...

204
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:14,780
How boring!

205
00:20:15,190 --> 00:20:19,490
I thought it'd be more dramatic,
with them screaming in agony.

206
00:20:21,450 --> 00:20:23,450
I've got places to be!

207
00:20:23,450 --> 00:20:26,250
This fool of a lord is really milking it!

208
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:29,170
Damn you!

209
00:20:34,090 --> 00:20:36,340
Who did you call a fool?!

210
00:20:36,340 --> 00:20:39,430
Say that again, and I will end you!

211
00:20:41,890 --> 00:20:43,010
Stop...

212
00:20:43,010 --> 00:20:44,720
What's with that woman?

213
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,890
Watch out!

214
00:20:45,890 --> 00:20:47,230
She's got a sword!

215
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:49,310
A kunoichi?!

216
00:20:52,190 --> 00:20:54,020
Captain, it's Shinobu!

217
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:57,030
Why is she making a scene?

218
00:20:59,740 --> 00:21:02,120
How dare you insult Lord Oden?!

219
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:07,040
You know nothing!

220
00:21:14,250 --> 00:21:16,340
You are the real fools!

221
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:24,800
Do you not understand that you
owe your peaceful lives to him?!

222
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:28,980
If we lose Lord Oden today...

223
00:21:28,980 --> 00:21:31,390
you will come to see...

224
00:21:31,810 --> 00:21:35,440
all the suffering he has
been shielding you from!

225
00:21:39,360 --> 00:21:43,160
Orochi is neither shogun nor dictator!

226
00:21:44,030 --> 00:21:47,580
Become a leader was never his purpose!

227
00:22:02,050 --> 00:22:03,220
Listen!

228
00:22:03,220 --> 00:22:07,010
To me, every single person in this country...

229
00:22:07,430 --> 00:22:11,180
is a sinner guilty of persecuting
the Kurozumi Clan.

230
00:22:11,890 --> 00:22:15,730
I'd be content to see them all die!

231
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:20,150
I became the shogun...

232
00:22:20,990 --> 00:22:24,610
to destroy this country!

233
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:27,870
That will complete my vengeance!

234
00:22:35,130 --> 00:22:39,380
Years ago, my damn grandpa
wanted to be shogun!

235
00:22:40,210 --> 00:22:42,840
This was before you were born.

236
00:22:43,260 --> 00:22:49,470
He was made to commit seppuku
for killing the other daimyo one by one!

237
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:55,480
Our clan fell from grace,
and it should have ended there.

238
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:57,230
But it didn't!

239
00:22:57,230 --> 00:23:01,320
The nightmare had just begun
for the Kurozumi Clan!

240
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:14,620
His surviving relatives were
hunted down by faceless vigilantes.

241
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:16,580
They beat us...

242
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:18,340
threw us in rivers...

243
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:20,170
and killed us!

244
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:25,630
I couldn't sleep because I was terrified
of their idiotic mob justice!

245
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:33,560
The man who had committed the crime
was already long dead!

246
00:23:34,100 --> 00:23:35,980
He's a Kurozumi!

247
00:23:35,980 --> 00:23:38,360
We'll make you pay!

248
00:23:47,610 --> 00:23:51,450
– You're related to the daimyo slayer!
– You're related to the daimyo slayer!

249
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:58,080
Stop!

250
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:04,760
Apparently, even a child can be a criminal
if they happen to be a Kurozumi!

251
00:24:04,760 --> 00:24:08,640
That's why everyone in Wano...

252
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:13,010
will suffer my wrath!

253
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:20,810
Wh-What the...?

254
00:24:22,610 --> 00:24:24,900
What are you going to do with them?!

255
00:24:28,610 --> 00:24:31,700
You reap what you sow!

256
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:38,460
Orochi! Why have you brought them here?!

257
00:24:39,370 --> 00:24:41,670
That side room contained...

258
00:24:42,210 --> 00:24:44,420
a great stockpile of weapons...

259
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:47,720
and hundreds of kidnapped hostages!

260
00:24:52,010 --> 00:24:53,930
Once they were handed over...

261
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:58,350
their lives as humans were over!

262
00:25:01,810 --> 00:25:03,520
They were all...

263
00:25:03,940 --> 00:25:06,570
tributes to Kaido!

264
00:25:10,820 --> 00:25:12,740
Those people will be...

265
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:16,160
sold, toyed with...

266
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:18,410
and killed!

267
00:25:21,370 --> 00:25:23,210
Lord Oden became furious!

268
00:25:23,630 --> 00:25:27,460
But that was when Orochi made an offer!

269
00:25:29,010 --> 00:25:32,090
You want to stop the kidnappings, Oden?!

270
00:25:33,390 --> 00:25:37,020
If you go to war with us now,

271
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:41,060
you'll lose more than you can imagine!

272
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:49,030
This vengeful man was
never interested in our land!

273
00:25:49,690 --> 00:25:54,660
So it was clear that even if we won,
the country would be devastated.

274
00:25:54,660 --> 00:25:58,790
That is why Lord Oden accepted his offer.

275
00:25:59,950 --> 00:26:05,290
He danced naked every week at the appointed time
to express his apology to the Kurozumi Clan.

276
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:08,670
While he knew he would lose everything,

277
00:26:08,670 --> 00:26:13,090
he could save a hundred lives
with each dance performance!

278
00:26:13,090 --> 00:26:14,470
– What?!
– What?!

279
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:25,400
They said when the ship
they were building was complete,

280
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,980
they would leave the country.

281
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:30,940
He took them at their word!

282
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:34,360
He visited each region weekly...

283
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:37,410
to check that everyone was all right!

284
00:26:39,950 --> 00:26:45,040
Lord Oden has always been
protecting this country!

285
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:48,090
Now, can you still call him a fool?!

286
00:26:48,090 --> 00:26:50,000
Tell me!

287
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:24,660
Lord Oden was protecting us?!

288
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:26,500
You say all this now...

289
00:27:26,500 --> 00:27:28,790
It's just a lot to take in!

290
00:27:32,710 --> 00:27:34,470
Fukurokuju!

291
00:27:35,430 --> 00:27:38,680
The truth only confuses matters.

292
00:27:39,390 --> 00:27:41,310
Let go of me!

293
00:27:41,310 --> 00:27:44,770
"The foolish lord met his end
after rebelling against the shogun."

294
00:27:44,770 --> 00:27:49,690
That will be common knowledge
once this execution is over.

295
00:27:50,860 --> 00:27:53,610
You knew the consequences, right?!

296
00:27:53,990 --> 00:27:57,240
I am ready to share their fate!

297
00:27:57,660 --> 00:27:59,910
I am Lord Oden's retainer!

298
00:27:59,910 --> 00:28:04,120
I will not obey anyone
who has become Orochi's dogs!

299
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:09,080
If anything happens to Lord Oden
and his men, I will die right alongside them!

300
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:15,130
No! It will not come to that!
We will survive and cast you down!

301
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,180
In your dreams.

302
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:21,680
Sh-Shogun Orochi!

303
00:28:22,220 --> 00:28:24,680
Please stop this execution!

304
00:28:28,270 --> 00:28:30,060
– We're begging you!
– We're begging you!

305
00:28:38,360 --> 00:28:40,070
Th-They need treatment now!

306
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:49,620
Orochi!

307
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:53,670
Scum, all of them.

308
00:28:54,170 --> 00:28:56,260
The Kurozumi endured persecution,

309
00:28:56,260 --> 00:29:00,800
not only from the shogun's family
but from the commoners as well.

310
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:08,890
So the crowd instantly understood that
Orochi's vengeance would spare no one.

311
00:29:11,060 --> 00:29:12,560
Meanwhile...

312
00:29:13,190 --> 00:29:18,440
the truth behind Oden's five-year
stretch of odd behavior and naked dances...

313
00:29:18,990 --> 00:29:22,410
spread among the people in no time.

314
00:29:22,410 --> 00:29:23,410
What?!

315
00:29:23,530 --> 00:29:28,160
That means he saved us back then.

316
00:29:29,330 --> 00:29:33,580
Yet we mocked him so much!

317
00:29:33,580 --> 00:29:37,420
His burden was greater than anyone's!

318
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:38,670
Damn it all!

319
00:29:38,670 --> 00:29:40,800
We're the worst!

320
00:29:42,390 --> 00:29:45,930
Everyone rushed to Oden.

321
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:51,480
They finally realized that the man in front of them,

322
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:56,690
the one facing death
in this protracted execution,

323
00:29:56,690 --> 00:30:01,030
was Wano's only hope.

324
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:05,490
Lord Oden, you must survive!

325
00:30:05,490 --> 00:30:08,450
I'm sorry for cursing you in my ignorance!

326
00:30:08,450 --> 00:30:11,160
Thank you for protecting us!

327
00:30:17,210 --> 00:30:19,210
Oh, now they care?!

328
00:30:19,210 --> 00:30:21,220
Those brown-nosers!

329
00:30:22,050 --> 00:30:23,380
Lord Oden, ignore–

330
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:25,220
Thank you all!

331
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:27,140
I will do my best!

332
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:29,390
So earnest!

333
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:32,810
However...

334
00:30:32,810 --> 00:30:38,780
Orochi couldn't let
the people's excitement stand.

335
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:42,030
And before they knew it,

336
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:47,780
they were surrounded by Kaido
and Orochi's armed subordinates.

337
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:56,170
The temperature of the oil had surpassed
700 degrees and continued to rise.

338
00:31:03,170 --> 00:31:07,470
Arrows spread the word
to every castle in each region.

